            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c896a6cf8f21d3f4-672b69 twpub-c896a6cf8f21d3f4-f1495c twpub-c896a6cf8f21d3f4-6b4cd0\"><table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000018\">PROLOGUE</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000031\">CHAPTER I. An Early Fright</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000080\">CHAPTER II. A Guest</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000181\">CHAPTER III. We Compare Notes</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000312\">CHAPTER IV. Her Habits—A Saunter</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000495\">CHAPTER V. A Wonderful Likeness</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000590\">CHAPTER VI. A Very Strange Agony</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000661\">CHAPTER VII. Descending</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000760\">CHAPTER VIII. Search</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000821\">CHAPTER IX. The Doctor</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000948\">CHAPTER X. Bereaved</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000001001\">CHAPTER XI. The Story</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000001076\">CHAPTER XII. A Petition</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000001145\">CHAPTER XIII. The Woodman</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000001222\">CHAPTER XIV. The Meeting</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000001287\">CHAPTER XV. Ordeal and Execution</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000001336\">CHAPTER XVI. Conclusion</$link></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000000016": {
