            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c896a6cf8f21d3f4/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c896a6cf8f21d3f4-672b69 twpub-c896a6cf8f21d3f4-f1495c twpub-c896a6cf8f21d3f4-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c13\"><div class=\"c2\">Project Gutenberg™ eBooks are often created from several printed editions, all of which are confirmed as not protected by copyright in the U.S. unless a copyright notice is included. Thus, we do not necessarily keep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</div></div></div>"
        },
